---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — LocalResizer" description="Learn about LocalResizer, a free browser-based image processing tool that prioritizes your privacy.">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 prose prose-slate">
    <h1>About LocalResizer</h1>
    <p>LocalResizer is a free online image processing tool that works entirely in your browser. Unlike traditional image tools that upload your files to remote servers, LocalResizer processes everything locally on your device.</p>
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <p>We use the browser's native Canvas API and modern compression algorithms to resize and compress your images. When you drop a file into our tool, it never leaves your computer — all processing happens right in your browser tab.</p>
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>We believe image processing should be fast, free, and private. No accounts, no watermarks, no data collection. Just drag, process, and download.</p>
    <h2>Supported Formats</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>JPEG</strong> — Lossy compression with quality control</li>
      <li><strong>PNG</strong> — Lossless format with transparency support</li>
      <li><strong>WebP</strong> — Modern format with superior compression</li>
      <li><strong>GIF</strong> — Animation support (coming soon)</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions or feedback? Reach us at <a href="/contact">our contact page</a>.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
